title: [Jeria's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a glaes-skylit ceiling, a ruby-eyed bleached skull hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A carved haon armoire sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the rug-covered floor.

Beneath a glaes-skylit ceiling, a ruby-eyed bleached skull hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A large carved haon table and a carved haon armoire sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on a colorful rug-covered floor.
